Data in Transit & At Rest: Network pe data bhejne ke waqt TLS/IPsec se secure kiya, aur storage mein full disk encryption daalaâ€”jaise apne data ka locker banaya!
Access Control: Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) lagaya, matlab har bande ko uske kaam ke hisaab se hi data ka darwaza kholne ka haq diya. Least privilege ka rule: zaroori ho utna hi access, zyada nahi!
Geofencing: Location ke hisaab se access set kiyaâ€”jaise agar office ke bahar ho toh sensitive data ka gate bandh!
PKI & Certificates: Certificate Authority banaya taaki encryption keys aur trust ka pura bandobast hoâ€”like digital muhar lagao!
Physical Security: CCTV aur biometric locks ke baare mein seekhaâ€”jaise ghar mein camera aur fingerprint lock lagate hai.
